messages.message: Hey team, I have an issue in UAT where I'm not getting the top menu bar with 'file' etc on any of the apps. This is on firefox
the left menu is also missing
This is intentional to block people from seeing the dock in case they land outside of aihub

Ok thanks. I'm developing an app and trying to open refiner which keeps spinning. The instructions tell me to click file -> open folder to be able to view the correct data. Is there a way around this without the menus?

Since Top bar is hidden, to open the existing refiner using Text Editor and add the path to process_files
      `"devInput": {`
    `"inputPath": "balaram/my-repo/fs/Instabase Drive/aihub/6a37bed6-75dd-4e11-b0e9-e9115ea53264/flows/1685596238149/out/s1_process_files"`
    `}`
